<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your OTP Code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #ebf8ff;
            color: #1a202c;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #3B82F6;
        }
        p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .otp {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #3B82F6;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #4a5568;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Your OTP Code</h1>
        <p>Your OTP code for password reset is:</p>
        <p class="otp"><%= otp %></p>
        <p>This code is valid for 10 minutes.</p>
        <p class="footer">Best regards, <br/> The Quick-Pay Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
